title: Acreage of Ten Crops for United States
notes:
Data Were Computed By Adding Barley, Buckwheat, Tame Hay, Rye, And Tobacco To The Five Crops Of Series 01037E -- Wheat, Oats, Cotton, Potatoes, And Corn. Source: Computed By NBER From U.S. Department Of Agriculture, "Agricultural Statistics, 1941, 1942, 1945; Except 1866-1910 Data For Wheat Acreage, Which Are From The Food Research Institute, "Wheat Studies", June 1926.

This NBER data series a01037f appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.

NBER Indicator: a01037f
